kieker.analysis.stage.select.timestampfilter

Class TimestampFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.CompositeStage
      • kieker.analysis.stage.select.timestampfilter.TimestampFilter

  • public class TimestampFilter
extends teetime.framework.CompositeStage
    Allows to filter IMonitoringRecord objects based on their given timestamps. This class has several specialized internal filters to distinguish different timestamps for different record types. It has one input port and two output ports. If the received record is within the defined timestamps, the object is delivered unmodified to the recordsWithinTimePeriodOutputPort, otherwise to the recordsOutsideTimePeriodOutputPort.
    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Andre van Hoorn, Jan Waller, Lars Bluemke
